{"id":73846,"title":"Robotic approaches to the neck.","abstract":"This article introduces and evaluates the feasibility of robot-assisted neck dissection as well as robot-assisted neck surgery via a modified facelift or retroauricular approach. Robot-assisted neck surgery is feasible compared with conventional techniques and shows a clear cosmetic benefit. ","date":"2014-06-02","categories":"Neoplasms","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24882801","annotations":[{"name":"Cosmetics","weight":0.0805305,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cosmetics"},{"name":"Neck","weight":0.0561009,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neck"},{"name":"Surgery","weight":0.0494293,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surgery"},{"name":"Robotics","weight":0.0370044,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robotics"},{"name":"Neck dissection","weight":0.0297972,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neck_dissection"},{"name":"Dissection","weight":0.0269662,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dissection"},{"name":"Envelope detector","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Envelope_detector"},{"name":"Rhytidectomy","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rhytidectomy"},{"name":"Medicine","weight":0.0143213,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medicine"}]}
